Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto six incomplete lines of what appears to be a letter or a report. On the verso four incomplete lines of a text of unknown character, -written over a washed-out text in three horizontal columns (dividing lines in red).
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (136368) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/136368)
